    "body": "PR #10617 adds host memory oom handling for GpuRowToColumnarExec.  Most of the support is actually contained in `GpuColumnarBatchBuilder`.  A new constructor does pre-allocation of host memory, instead of the default on-demand growth. \r\n There are other places in the code where `GpuColumnarBatchBuilder` is used.  We should consider converting these to use the pre-allocation version and add host memory oom handling for them.\r\n\r\n- HostColumnarToGpu\r\n- ParquetCachedBatchSerializer\r\n- InternalColumnarRddConverter\r\n\r\n",
